description: Geaux-Yo is the healthy alternative to ice cream for your summer sweet tooth cravings. Our premium frozen yogurts are made from the highest quality ingredients. Good for your tummy and a perfect cure for your sweet tooth. Our many flavors, toppings and treats are served on location all across Baton Rouge.We are the 1st Premium Frozen Yogurt Truck to hit Baton Rouge. Come join the Food Truck Revolution!
